    "body": "This is because supports-color uses a [`browser` field](https://github.com/defunctzombie/package-browser-field-spec):\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/chalk/supports-color/blob/651576a5fabfa489660b48f50a7f2e5ed7676997/package.json#L52\r\n\r\nThat line tells browserify to use this file instead of index.js:\r\nhttps://github.com/chalk/supports-color/blob/master/browser.js\r\n\r\nIf you are not bundling code for the browser, you can use the --no-browser-field flag.",
